citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
The licensee was in travel status on the day of the inspection and had not submitted any travel itinerary to the
Regional Office. According to a person at site 001, the licensee was exhibiting elsewhere and they had no
information as to when he might return.
